→ 200, `/charts` → 200, `/dashboards/018f5e4a-2c10-7a3b-9d40-3f1c8b9a2e77` (seeded "Onboarding funnel —
Q2") → 200. Password protection is a manual dashboard step the user completes separately (plan/billing-
